== Overview
I'm a superfan of Chinese Rap. It's my spiritual coffee. I would like to share some of my favorite Rappers and their hightlights here. (排名不分先后，注意，不分先后)

== Chinese Rappers
- *Masiwei*\n
Performance in mixture of classic and rap, a real masterpice, including: /Never Sleep/, /The Dawn/, and /Hip-Hop Saved My Life/ . \[[https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV1164y197qC?from=search&seid=13854811123149076406&spm_id_from=333.337.0.0 video]\] \n
King of flow: /Toban Djan/. \[[https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV1Dy4y1a7kx?from=search&seid=3694769173977747062&spm_id_from=333.337.0.0 video]\] \n
Some lyrics I like:\n
/我不要你变成*祝英台*, 我们感情不需要打*苦情牌*, Cuz we stay *high* and we stay *fly*, 打响我们爱的战役*不停摆*/ (from /Unexpected Troubles/ \[[https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV16U4y1W7tY?from=search&seid=17885367245459276509&spm_id_from=333.337.0.0 video]\])

- *王闪火*\n
This sone literally resonates with me: /阿司匹林 (Aspirin)/ \[[https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV12E411y7Vn/?spm_id_from=333.788.recommend_more_video.0 original_version]\] \[[https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV1fV41117AV/?spm_id_from=333.788.recommend_more_video.-1 live]\]

- *姜云升*\n
His songs helped me survive NeurIPS'21 ddl. This is a \[[https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=MTQiZwZyTn8&t=195s collection]\] of his songs.\n 
Some lyrics I like:\n
/生命是没意义的因为你我终将死去，时间的长河会抹去你我存在的痕迹，可自从人们学会了相爱的那一刻起，我们因为对方的存在而获得了意义/ (from /你一定能够成为你想成为的人/) \n
/从咸阳机场出发追到*浦东门口*，你却和所有人说我们只是*普通朋友*/ (from /不后悔遇见你/)

